---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'quick-verdict', text: 'Quick Verdict', level: 2 },
  { id: 'comparison-table', text: 'Side-by-Side Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'cigna', text: 'Cigna Global', level: 2 },
  { id: 'bupa', text: 'Bupa Global', level: 2 },
  { id: 'allianz', text: 'Allianz Care', level: 2 },
  { id: 'pricing', text: 'Pricing Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'maternity-details', text: 'Maternity Coverage Details', level: 2 },
  { id: 'best-for', text: 'Which Is Best For You?', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'FAQs', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { href: '/insurance-for/families', text: 'Family Insurance Guide' },
  { href: '/guides/pregnancy-abroad-insurance', text: 'Pregnancy Abroad Guide' },
  { href: '/providers/cigna-global', text: 'Cigna Global Review' },
  { href: '/providers/bupa-global', text: 'Bupa Global Review' },
  { href: '/providers/allianz-care', text: 'Allianz Care Review' },
];

const mainComparisonColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'cigna', header: 'Cigna Global' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'Bupa Global' },
  { key: 'allianz', header: 'Allianz Care' },
];

const mainComparisonRows = [
  { feature: 'Waiting Period', cigna: '10-12 months', bupa: '12 months', allianz: '10-12 months' },
  { feature: 'Normal Delivery', cigna: 'Full coverage', bupa: 'Full coverage', allianz: 'Up to limits' },
  { feature: 'C-Section', cigna: 'Full coverage', bupa: 'Full coverage', allianz: 'Full coverage' },
  { feature: 'Complications', cigna: 'Full coverage', bupa: 'Full coverage', allianz: 'Full coverage' },
  { feature: 'Prenatal Care', cigna: 'Comprehensive', bupa: 'Comprehensive', allianz: 'Standard visits' },
  { feature: 'Postnatal Care', cigna: '6 weeks', bupa: '6-8 weeks', allianz: '6 weeks' },
  { feature: 'Newborn Coverage', cigna: '30 days auto', bupa: '14 days auto', allianz: '30 days auto' },
  { feature: 'Maternity Limit', cigna: '$15,000-30,000', bupa: 'Plan dependent', allianz: '$10,000-20,000' },
];

const pricingColumns = [
  { key: 'profile', header: 'Profile' },
  { key: 'cigna', header: 'Cigna Global' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'Bupa Global' },
  { key: 'allianz', header: 'Allianz Care' },
];

const pricingRows = [
  { profile: 'Woman (30) with maternity', cigna: '$450-600/mo', bupa: '$500-700/mo', allianz: '$380-520/mo' },
  { profile: 'Woman (35) with maternity', cigna: '$520-720/mo', bupa: '$580-800/mo', allianz: '$440-600/mo' },
  { profile: 'Couple (30s) with maternity', cigna: '$750-1,000/mo', bupa: '$850-1,150/mo', allianz: '$650-900/mo' },
  { profile: 'Maternity add-on cost', cigna: '+$150-200/mo', bupa: '+$180-250/mo', allianz: '+$120-180/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Cigna vs Bupa vs Allianz for Maternity Coverage | 2025 Comparison"
  description="Compare Cigna Global, Bupa Global, and Allianz Care for maternity coverage. Expert analysis of prenatal care, delivery, complications, and newborn coverage for expats."
  headline="Cigna vs Bupa vs Allianz: Best Maternity Coverage"
  subheadline="Complete comparison for expats planning pregnancy abroad—covering prenatal care, delivery options, complications, and newborn coverage."
  heroImage="/images/pages/provider-card-generic.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get Quotes"
  ctaButtonHref="/get-quotes"
>
  <section id="quick-verdict" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Quick Verdict</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-800 mb-2">Cigna Global</h3>
        <p class="text-primary-700 mb-3">Best Overall Maternity</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">Highest maternity limits, comprehensive prenatal, and 30-day automatic newborn coverage. The safest choice for expat pregnancies.</p>
        <a href="/providers/cigna-global" class="inline-block bg-primary-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-primary-700 transition text-sm" style="color: white !important;">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-800 mb-2">Bupa Global</h3>
        <p class="text-purple-700 mb-3">Best Hospital Network</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">Premium maternity hospitals worldwide with excellent midwife and birthing center options. Premium service experience.</p>
        <a href="/providers/bupa-global" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-purple-700 transition text-sm" style="color: white !important;">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">Allianz Care</h3>
        <p class="text-green-700 mb-3">Best Value</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">Good maternity coverage at the most affordable price. Solid choice for straightforward pregnancies in lower-cost countries.</p>
        <a href="/providers/allianz-care" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition text-sm" style="color: white !important;">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="comparison-table" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Side-by-Side Comparison</h2>
    <ComparisonTable columns={mainComparisonColumns} rows={mainComparisonRows} />
  </section>

  <section id="cigna" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Cigna Global</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Highest Limits</span>
      <span class="bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Full Prenatal</span>
      <span class="bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">30-Day Newborn</span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Cigna Global offers the most comprehensive maternity coverage among major international insurers. Limits range from $15,000 to $30,000 depending on plan level—sufficient for private hospital deliveries in most countries, including Singapore, UAE, and Hong Kong where costs are highest.</p>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Prenatal care is comprehensive: all standard ultrasounds, screenings, and consultations are covered. The 30-day automatic newborn coverage is the longest in the industry, giving you time to add your baby to the policy without gaps. Complications are fully covered regardless of maternity limits.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">Maternity Strengths</h4>
        <ul class="text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• Highest maternity limits ($15K-30K)</li>
          <li>• Comprehensive prenatal coverage</li>
          <li>• 30-day automatic newborn cover</li>
          <li>• Complications fully covered</li>
          <li>• Global network of maternity hospitals</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">Considerations</h4>
        <ul class="text-amber-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• 10-12 month waiting period</li>
          <li>• Higher premiums for maternity</li>
          <li>• Limits may not cover premium US hospitals</li>
          <li>• Fertility treatments excluded</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/providers/cigna-global" class="inline-block bg-primary-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Cigna Quote</a>
  </section>

  <section id="bupa" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Bupa Global</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Premium Hospitals</span>
      <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Midwife Options</span>
      <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Extended Postnatal</span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Bupa Global's maternity coverage emphasizes quality and choice. Their network includes renowned maternity hospitals worldwide, and coverage often extends to midwife-led care and birthing centers—options not always available with other insurers.</p>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Postnatal coverage extends up to 8 weeks, longer than competitors, which helps with recovery support and newborn check-ups. The 12-month waiting period is standard. While their 14-day automatic newborn coverage is shorter than Cigna's 30 days, adding your baby is straightforward.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">Maternity Strengths</h4>
        <ul class="text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• Premium maternity hospital network</li>
          <li>• Midwife and birthing center coverage</li>
          <li>• Extended postnatal care (8 weeks)</li>
          <li>• Excellent UK/EU maternity facilities</li>
          <li>• Care coordinator support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">Considerations</h4>
        <ul class="text-amber-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• Highest maternity premiums</li>
          <li>• 12-month waiting period strict</li>
          <li>• 14-day newborn auto-cover (shorter)</li>
          <li>• Limits vary significantly by plan</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/providers/bupa-global" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-700 transition font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Bupa Quote</a>
  </section>

  <section id="allianz" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Allianz Care</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Most Affordable</span>
      <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Good Coverage</span>
      <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">30-Day Newborn</span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Allianz Care provides solid maternity coverage at the most accessible price point. Limits of $10,000-20,000 are adequate for deliveries in most countries outside of premium markets (UAE, Singapore, US). If you're giving birth in Europe, Asia, or Latin America, Allianz usually suffices.</p>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Prenatal care covers standard visits and screenings, though some advanced tests may require pre-approval. The 30-day automatic newborn coverage matches Cigna's industry-leading period. For straightforward pregnancies with budget considerations, Allianz delivers value.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">Maternity Strengths</h4>
        <ul class="text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• Most affordable maternity premiums</li>
          <li>• Adequate limits for most countries</li>
          <li>• 30-day automatic newborn cover</li>
          <li>• Complications fully covered</li>
          <li>• Flexible plan options</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">Considerations</h4>
        <ul class="text-amber-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• Lower limits ($10K-20K)</li>
          <li>• Standard prenatal only</li>
          <li>• Limited premium hospital access</li>
          <li>• May need pre-approval for tests</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/providers/allianz-care" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Allianz Quote</a>
  </section>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Maternity Coverage Quotes"
    description="Get personalized quotes with maternity benefits from all three providers."
    buttonText="Get Free Quotes"
    buttonHref="/get-quotes"
  />

  <section id="pricing" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Pricing Comparison</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">Maternity coverage significantly increases premiums—plan ahead:</p>
    <ComparisonTable columns={pricingColumns} rows={pricingRows} />
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-4">*Maternity is typically an add-on with 10-12 month waiting periods. You must have coverage before conception for benefits to apply. Prices exclude US coverage.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="maternity-details" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Maternity Coverage Details</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-3">What's Typically Covered</h3>
        <ul class="text-neutral-700 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>• Prenatal consultations</li>
          <li>• Ultrasounds and screenings</li>
          <li>• Hospital delivery (vaginal/C-section)</li>
          <li>• Anesthesia and medications</li>
          <li>• Complications and emergencies</li>
          <li>• Postnatal check-ups</li>
          <li>• Newborn initial coverage</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-3">What's Usually Excluded</h3>
        <ul class="text-neutral-700 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>• Fertility treatments (IVF, IUI)</li>
          <li>• Surrogacy</li>
          <li>• Elective C-sections (some plans)</li>
          <li>• Home births (some plans)</li>
          <li>• Pregnancy before waiting period</li>
          <li>• Non-medically necessary tests</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-3">Critical Timing Considerations</h3>
      <p class="text-blue-700 mb-4">The waiting period is strictly enforced. Here's what you need to know:</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">Before Conception</h4>
          <ul class="text-blue-700 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• Must have maternity coverage before getting pregnant</li>
            <li>• 10-12 month waiting period starts at policy inception</li>
            <li>• Cannot add maternity after conception</li>
            <li>• Plan 12-15 months ahead of desired pregnancy</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">During Pregnancy</h4>
          <ul class="text-blue-700 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• Prenatal care begins after positive test</li>
            <li>• Pre-authorize expensive tests if required</li>
            <li>• Choose delivery hospital early</li>
            <li>• Understand newborn enrollment process</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="best-for" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Which Is Best For You?</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="bg-primary-50 border-l-4 border-primary-600 p-4">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary-800 mb-2">Choose Cigna Global if:</h3>
        <ul class="text-primary-700 space-y-1">
          <li>• You want the highest maternity limits</li>
          <li>• Comprehensive prenatal care matters</li>
          <li>• 30-day newborn auto-cover is valuable</li>
          <li>• You're in a high-cost delivery market</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-600 p-4">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-800 mb-2">Choose Bupa Global if:</h3>
        <ul class="text-purple-700 space-y-1">
          <li>• Premium hospital access matters most</li>
          <li>• You want midwife or birthing center options</li>
          <li>• Extended postnatal care is important</li>
          <li>• You're based in UK or Europe</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-600 p-4">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">Choose Allianz Care if:</h3>
        <ul class="text-green-700 space-y-1">
          <li>• Budget is a significant factor</li>
          <li>• You're in a moderate-cost country</li>
          <li>• $10K-20K limits are sufficient</li>
          <li>• You expect a straightforward pregnancy</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="faqs" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Can I add maternity coverage after I'm pregnant?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">No. Pregnancy is considered a pre-existing condition once you conceive. You must have maternity coverage in place before becoming pregnant, and the waiting period (10-12 months) must be completed before delivery for benefits to apply.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-2">What if there are complications?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">Complications are typically covered fully, regardless of maternity sub-limits. If you develop gestational diabetes, preeclampsia, or require an emergency C-section, these are covered under your main medical benefits, not your maternity limit. Always confirm with your insurer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-2">How do I add my newborn to my policy?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">Notify your insurer within the automatic coverage period (14-30 days). They'll add your baby to your policy—typically at a prorated premium for the first year. If you miss the deadline, you may need medical underwriting and could face coverage gaps.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Are home births or water births covered?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">Coverage varies. Bupa is most likely to cover midwife-attended home births and birthing centers. Cigna and Allianz typically focus on hospital deliveries. If you want alternative birth settings, verify coverage before choosing a plan.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="bg-neutral-100 rounded-lg p-6 text-sm text-neutral-600">
    <p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Maternity coverage, limits, and waiting periods vary by specific plan and region. Insurance terms change frequently. Always verify current maternity benefits, waiting periods, and newborn coverage directly with providers before purchasing. This comparison is for informational purposes only.</p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
